title: Paul Print - Only Me ...!
description:
The Debut E.P. \\\"Only Me ...!\\\" from the up and coming Indie/Alternative artist Paul Print.
Stripped down to acoustic guitar and vocals. Paul shows he has catchy songwriting skills of  the greats of today and yesteryear with a unique engageging, powerful, soulful vocal that will send shivers down your spine.

If you like anything from the 60\\\&#039;s such as the Beatles, Kinks, Small Faces then you will like this .. also there are great similarities in vibe to Nirvana Unplugged and  acoustic sets from american rock bands of the 70\\\&#039;s, due to it\\\&#039;s stripped down essence.

check his myspace for his up to date and full band tunes.
